# {{ .Name }} ({{ .Type }})

Declares a plugin catalog entry inside a registry. Think of this as the named slot in the
registry that will hold one or more versions. Users browse and install from this entry.

The registry itself is managed by [`cycloid_plugin_registry`](plugin_registry); versions
are published with [`cycloid_plugin_version`](plugin_version).

